<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/565005803/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """The methodooly is learning by doing. then students should develop a mechatronics prototype to provide a creative solution to a challenge. The students will work in groups and during the course, there will be deadlines to deliver some part of the project.
Each deliverable will be a technical report including sketches of the potential solutions, mathematical analysis, blueprints, etc.
The final solution will be presented and the group will do a demo of the solution.
1. Mandatory deliverables provided by students: 50%
2. Final demonstration: 50%

Extraordinary examan evaluation consist in the individual new mechatronics project development by the student containing the deliverables and final demostration."""@es .

